          <h3 class='text-2xl font-display text-brand-blue mb-6'>For Teens</h3>
          <ul class='space-y-4'>
            <li class='flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-blue/70'>
              <svg
                class='w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-1'
                fill='currentColor'
                viewBox='0 0 20 20'
                ><path
                  fill-rule='evenodd'
                  d='M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z'
                  clip-rule='evenodd'></path></svg
              >
              Feeling understood and supported
            </li>
            <li class='flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-blue/70'>
              <svg
                class='w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-1'
                fill='currentColor'
                viewBox='0 0 20 20'
                ><path
                  fill-rule='evenodd'
